{"tid":898453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星巴克前CEO考慮2020年競選美總統","createTime":"2018-11-11T16:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T16:47:50.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"696be56c611758e46053203d10b232f60675040f","tid":898453,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/11/10/1988873_d9deeaec7d8a195a5caf7b553706074b_320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F1988873_d9deeaec7d8a195a5caf7b553706074b_320.jpg&h=8e08bdb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國咖啡連鎖店星巴克(Starbucks)前主席兼行政總裁舒爾茨(Howard Schultz)正組建一支公關團隊，準備出版一本具有公民意識的新書，並考慮在2020年競選總統。<br />\nCNBC報道，在舒爾茨公關團隊名單中，被喻為共和黨策略師的施密特(Steve Schmidt)是關鍵人物，他曾擔任公關公司愛德曼(Edelman)的副主席，曾在2008年領導共和黨參議員麥凱恩(John McCain)的總統競選活動。<br />\n報道指，舒爾茨是眾多被廣泛認為有能力挑戰特朗普的候選人之一，其主要在商界而非政治領域有經驗，倘若要競選總統寶座，可能需要有經驗的政治家協助，而施密特便是合適人選。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1988873/%E6%98%9F%E5%B7%B4%E5%85%8B%E5%89%8DCEO%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE2020%E5%B9%B4%E7%AB%B6%E9%81%B8%E7%BE%8E%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1988873%2F%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%2585%258B%25E5%2589%258DCEO%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE2020%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1&d=BpzTxVwg9Yz0Kk8kJrbz2iwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=382508c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1988873/%E6%98%9F%E5%B7%B4%E5%85%8B%E5%89%8DCEO%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE2020%E5%B9%B4%E7%AB%B6%E9%81%B8%E7%BE%8E%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1</a><br />\n下屆好多有錢佬選總統<br />\n<br />\n前星巴克CEO,彭博,TRUMP 全部都係有錢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9810bc3342458a229a27080d9aa4dd3831accc23","tid":898453,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"算9數啦叫條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f807a7c64f160a08f38bc0ae33a3211eb597b95","tid":898453,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:47:50.000Z","msg":"呢個世界需要一個枱面偏左枱底偏右既人做總統"}]}